{"tid":649923,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]  李嘉欣返石澳別墅嘆世界","createTime":"2018-05-02T01:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T07:47:28.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"911c3e9733ef46e07c58957126237f3ea445d0f6","tid":649923,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:53:06.000Z","msg":"昨日假期，天朗氣清，最適宜郊遊，如果自己有間望海嘅別墅，就更加係無敵啦！不過唔係普通人可以享有。大美人李嘉欣就唔同喇！嘉欣昨日在instagram貼相，hang tag「 #labourday #thankful #whereigotmarried #perfectday #我真係恭喜你呀」，喺一個綠草如茵嘅大花園，背景係一大片海，加埋藍天白雲，展望明日有幾陣驟雨，隨後兩三日天色逐漸好轉。同狗狗一齊同陽光玩遊戲，真係羨慕死人。<br />\n<br />\n嘉欣畀晒提示#whereigotmarried，嘉欣同老公許晉亨2008年結婚時，就係喺老爺許世勳當時名下嘅石澳別墅舉行億元婚禮。昨日勞動假，囝囝Jayden唔使返學，一家人去別墅玩吓休息吓，都咪話唔疏干。<br />\n<br />\n相中見着住淺藍色裙，戴白色帽嘅嘉欣，踎低摸緊愛犬個頭，襯托埋咁好嘅天氣，好有夏天feel。唔知張相係老公定囝囝操刀影呢。"},{"pid":"be5da2bd70c5973ff9d3228d24f1916970f29fec","tid":649923,"uid":73803,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:04:19.000Z","msg":"睇錯李嘉誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0abe62e76c68cfb1f686b7fdb4e6031d992f2d4","tid":649923,"uid":35070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"好似人地王晶咁癡心情長劍咁"},{"pid":"3676ff446128d336d7e0230e95b2d80d5f405bc5","tid":649923,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"個POST應該好嘈"},{"pid":"aa8ff8167e1b495046ec91f4a5da09fccc6f5b79","tid":649923,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"hang tag"},{"pid":"f0ba218fdf6a5a429d8cd4df4c26832832aeda62","tid":649923,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8ff8167e1b495046ec91f4a5da09fccc6f5b79","tid":649923,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"hang tag"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:10:43.000Z","msg":"goodest english 文盲妓者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec188f6